BT /F2 16 Tf 54.00 599.25 Td (1. What CarryLink Does) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 564.00 Td (CarryLink is a peer-to-peer travel delivery matching website. It helps people who live outside their home) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 549.00 Td (countries connect with travelers already going between two places.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 525.75 Td (Example: a Lebanese person living in Canada wants to send a small gift, document, or package to Lebanon.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 510.75 Td (Instead of using expensive international shipping, the sender can find a traveler going from Canada to) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 495.75 Td (Lebanon and agree on handoff details, compensation, and delivery details.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 472.50 Td (CarryLink can also work in the opposite direction, such as Lebanon to Canada, or for other international) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 457.50 Td (routes.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 434.25 Td (CarryLink is a matching and communication platform. It does not inspect items, does not guarantee) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 419.25 Td (delivery, and does not replace airline, airport, customs, or destination-country rules.) Tj ET
