BT /F2 12 Tf 54.00 189.00 Td (Traveler or Carrier) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 160.75 Td (A traveler is already traveling between two places and may have available luggage space. A traveler can:) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66.00 137.50 Td (- Post a trip.) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 66.00 122.50 Td (- State origin, destination, travel dates, and available space.) Tj ET
