BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 646.50 Td (and arriving May 21. I prefer pickup near YUL or downtown Montreal. Please confirm the exact contents and) Tj ET
BT /F1 10 Tf 54.00 631.50 Td (whether customs declaration is needed.) Tj ET
